{"type": "article", "id": 4846, "title": "Re-cinto 沙发", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-31T08:32:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060614363791GgERBn5tvDIlfL.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t意大利初创品牌 Davide Anzalone 推出了一款名为「Re-cinto」的沙发，设计师将其看作是一款具有休闲精神的沙发，由外部胶合板制成的沙发结构与像浮岛一般的中央座位区构成。沙发两侧与背面之间形成的空隙用一排靠垫进行填充，作为扶手和靠背，而在座位下方，还提供了存储收纳空间。这样的结构有助于使用者发挥自己的想像力，既可以将靠垫通通撤去，亦可以为靠垫选择不同颜色的外包装，改变沙发的整体风格。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143634utqzNSnr2bm58ydC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143635AzWZmkK4TPtYGwuc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143635k64MIo1nT93R0bGK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143636LeOnSGZHVgIu6Jjm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606143637yiUpf3HW2brKwOTc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}